          "text": "To enjoy coffee in a healthy way, consider the following tips:\n\n1. **Limit Sugar and Sweeteners**: Minimize adding sugar or artificial sweeteners. Opt for natural alternatives like a touch of cinnamon or vanilla extract if you need extra flavor.\n\n2. **Choose Healthy Additives**: Use a splash of milk or plant-based milk instead of creamers that might contain added sugars and fats.\n\n3. **Moderate Your Intake**: Aim for moderate consumption, typically 3-4 cups per day, depending on individual tolerance and health conditions.\n\n4. **Mind the Timing**: Avoid coffee too late in the day to prevent it from disrupting sleep.\n\n5. **Stay Hydrated**: Drink water alongside your coffee to stay hydrated.\n\n6. **Quality Over Quantity**: Choose high-quality, organic coffee beans to reduce exposure to pesticides and toxins.\n\n7. **Listen to Your Body**: Pay attention to how your body reacts and adjust your intake as needed.\n\nBy making these mindful choices, you can enjoy your coffee while supporting your health."
